@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram

[*] --> AssignStaffMember

state "Unassigned" as Unassigned
state "Assigned" as Assigned
state "Switching" as Switching
state "Removed" as Removed
state "Archived" as Archived

AssignStaffMember : entry / assign staff member to client or campaign
AssignStaffMember : do / add staff member to assignment
AssignStaffMember : exit / staff member assigned

Unassigned : entry / staff member not assigned
Unassigned : do / allow assigning staff member
Unassigned : exit / staff member assigned

Assigned : entry / staff member assigned
Assigned : do / enable switching between assignments
Assigned : exit / staff member switched to new assignment

Switching : entry / staff member switching assignments
Switching : do / update assignment records
Switching : exit / staff member switched successfully

Removed : entry / staff member removed from assignment
Removed : do / remove staff member from assignment
Removed : exit / staff member unassigned

Archived : entry / staff member archived
Archived : do / archive staff member record
Archived : exit / staff member record archived

AssignStaffMember --> Unassigned
Unassigned --> Assigned : [assign staff member]
Assigned --> Switching : [switch assignments]
Switching --> Assigned : [switch successful]
Assigned --> Removed : [remove from assignment]
Removed --> Unassigned : [unassigned]
Assigned --> Archived : [archive staff member]

@enduml
